          "text": "Once per battle, at the start of any phase, you can select one enemy unit (excluding MONSTERS and VEHICLES ) within 12\" of the bearer. That unit must take a Battle-shock test ; if that test is failed, until the end of your next turn, that unit cannot have the Benefit of Cover .",
